==Mandarin==

===Etymology===
Literally: 18,000 [[里|li]].

===Pronunciation===
[[Pinyin]]: shí wàn bā qīan lĭ

===Phrase===
'''[[十]][[万]][[八]][[千]][[里]]''' ([[Simplified Chinese]])

# (''idiom'') Used to describe a great distance.
([[Simplified Chinese]])

#: ''[[偶]][[从]]'''十万八千里'''[[的]][[地方]][[回来]][[了]].'' ([[Simplified Chinese]])

#: ''[[偶]][[從]]'''十萬八千里'''[[的]][[地方]][[回來]][[了]].'' ([[Traditional Chinese]])

# {{idiom}} Used to describe a huge difference between two things.

#: ''[[想象]][[真]][[的]][[会]][[离]][[事实]]'''十万八千里'''的！'' ([[Simplified Chinese]])

#: ''[[想像]][[真]][[的]][[會]][[離]][[事实|事實]]'''十萬八千里'''的！'' ([[Traditional Chinese]])

===Alternate forms===
[[十]][[萬]][[八]][[千]][[里]] ([[Traditional Chinese]])

